      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis benefits from proactive subframe reinforcement and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring the high-pressure variable valve timing remains within optimal parameters. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry remains tight, offering the precise turn-in and telepathic feedback characteristic of this platform. A mechanically robust specimen ready for the spirited driver.",
